	<h3>Trade till the final second</h3>
	<h4>What is BTX In-Play Trading?</h4>
	<p>We are the first in Binary Options market to implement this In-Play Trading system.

In-Play Trading is a trade that takes place after the 60 seconds options have started. Traders will be able to place a call or a put option at any point of time within the trading 60 seconds. Traders can even trade right up to the 59th second!
	</p>
	<h4>What is the main advantage of BTX In-Play Trading to the traders?</h4>
	<p>The In-Play Trading allows you to assess what's going on in the market before placing your trade. All the researches and reading of stats in the world can only get you to certain distance and sometimes it's preferable to just watch the last minute price movements before deciding which direction your money is on.</p>
